Class VerboseWorkSet<T>

java.lang.Object
  jpaul.DataStructs.VerboseWorkSet<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, WorkSet<T>
public class VerboseWorkSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements WorkSet<T>, java.io.Serializable

VerboseWorkSet - Debugging wrapper for a WorkSet. Prints helpful messages each time the state of the WorkSet is modified (ex: adding/extracting elements and when clearing the entire content of the WorkSet.).

Version:
